_sName: Our House, in the Middle of the Void
_sText:
Two mirrored buildings connected by a walkway, floating in a void.  

This is my first map, just playing around with brushes n blocks.  Made in Hammer++ over the course of a few hours, with a few additional hours spent troubleshooting why the spawns have to be floating in the air
